Interface TokenStream

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.Iterator<java.lang.String>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicTokenStream

    public interface TokenStream
extends java.util.Iterator<java.lang.String>
    Stream-like objects for reading Logo tokens.

    All methods for reading elements may throw IllegalStateException and NoSuchElementException if nessisary

    Author:
    Paul Yang
